    • Field Detail

      • HEAD

        public static final Slot HEAD
        Assumes heads and eyes are independent instead of worrying about complex scenarios. Valid example: a hat and lenses. Invalid example: A full-head helmet and googles.

      • EYES

        public static final Slot EYES
        See Also:
        HEAD

      • HAND

        public static final Slot HAND
        Assuming that whatever covers your whole hands will force you to remove anything that is on your fingers. It's easy to imagine cloth gloves and rings being worn together for example but less so when it comes to full battle gloves so to simplify we supposed the "magical hand energies" would eliminate each other..

      • FINGER

        public static final Slot FINGER
        Only one finger on each hand is allowed at a time. Hand items also need to be removed.
